author: A Correspondent
title: Sagar Pawar's brace wins it for Egyptian Boys
text: Thanks to Sagar Pawar's brace, Egyptian Boys fought well to carve out a close 3-2 win over Kalina Village Boys 'B' in an eighth round league match of the 15th Kalina Football League 2015, organised by the Our Lady of Egypt Church Sports Committee at the St Mary's High School ground, Kalina.
